snippet.title: Taiko Frenzy - Release Trailer | Meta Quest Store & Steam
snippet.description:
Version 1.0 of Taiko Frenzy, the VR rhythm game inspired by Japanese folklore is available now on:
Meta Quest Store
https://ocul.us/3oq1nNR
Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2680410/Taiko_Frenzy/

Drum up the beat, unleash your inner Taiko Master!
